title: The Denzels - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description:
The single "222" by The Denzels is this week's "Track of the Week". The band came to Converse Rubber Tracks and immediately jumped into exploring the use of different instruments and set-ups within the studio. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
